    "remark": {
      "title": "屋況介紹",
      "key": "remark",
      "active": 1,
      "content": "&lt;span&nbsp;style=&quot;font-family:'微軟正黑體','sans-serif';&quot;&gt;&lt;span&nbsp;style=&quot;font-size:16.0pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span&nbsp;style=&quot;color:blue;&quot;&gt;位於敦化北路222巷內,凱旋廣場大樓B1&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&nbsp;/&gt;&lt;br&nbsp;/&gt;&lt;span&nbsp;style=&quot;font-family:'微軟正黑體','sans-serif';&quot;&gt;&lt;span&nbsp;style=&quot;font-size:16.0pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span&nbsp;style=&quot;color:blue;&quot;&gt;捷運中山國中站.敦化北路.民生東路公車路線多.交通便捷.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&nbsp;/&gt;&lt;br&nbsp;/&gt;&lt;span&nbsp;style=&quot;font-family:'微軟正黑體','sans-serif';&quot;&gt;&lt;span&nbsp;style=&quot;font-size:16.0pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span&nbsp;style=&quot;color:blue;&quot;&gt;附近知名地標:長庚醫院.文華東方酒店.民生社區.慶城商圈.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&nbsp;/&gt;&lt;br&nbsp;/&gt;&lt;span&nbsp;style=&quot;font-family:'微軟正黑體','sans-serif';&quot;&gt;&lt;span&nbsp;style=&quot;font-size:16.0pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span&nbsp;style=&quot;color:blue;&quot;&gt;民族國小.中山國中,附近有敦北.民生公園.生活機能完善&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&nbsp;/&gt;&lt;br&nbsp;/&gt;&lt;span&nbsp;style=&quot;font-family:'微軟正黑體','sans-serif';&quot;&gt;&lt;span&nbsp;style=&quot;font-size:16.0pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span&nbsp;style=&quot;color:blue;&quot;&gt;格局方正.租金含水費.網路.管理費等,附冷氣.冰箱等部分傢俱.家電.電費依台電帳單,依用電比例負擔.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&nbsp;/&gt;&lt;br&nbsp;/&gt;&lt;span&nbsp;style=&quot;font-family:'微軟正黑體','sans-serif';&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&nbsp;/&gt;&lt;br&nbsp;/&gt;&lt;span&nbsp;style=&quot;font-family:'微軟正黑體','sans-serif';&quot;&gt;&lt;span&nbsp;style=&quot;font-size:20.0pt;&quot;&gt;看屋專線:0921-117-665朱先生&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&nbsp;/&gt;&lt;br&nbsp;/&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;span&nbsp;style=&quot;font-family:'微軟正黑體','sans-serif';&quot;&gt;&lt;span&nbsp;style=&quot;font-size:20.0pt;&quot;&gt;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;0983-252-618&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span&nbsp;style=&quot;font-family:'微軟正黑體','sans-serif';&quot;&gt;&lt;span